reviewtext: These tapes work. No problems with jamming in the VCR.  I bought Sony first, and I was surprised that they all were jamming up in two of my VCR.  After 5 of the Sony tapes jammed, I threw them all away. I have been using the TDK tapes for a while - no problems.  Would buy again.  Quick shipping.
summary: quick shipping - no problems with tapes.
